  "title": "Cybersecurity Director (Healthcare)",
  "description": "<p><strong>Our Client is one of the leading player in healthcare industry. Due to business needs, they are now recruiting a Cybersecurity Director to be part of their IT team for ongoing transformation projects. They are located in the Central Area - easily accessible.</strong></p><p><strong>Roles and Responsibilities:</strong></p><p><ul><li>Develop healthcare-focused security policies and frameworks, and oversee enterprise-wide risk management across group.</li><li>Drive strategic technology decisions by evaluating and implementing advanced cybersecurity solutions.</li><li>Lead cybersecurity governance for EMR systems, telehealth platforms, and medical device networks.</li><li>Build strong partnerships with MOH, Synapxe, and GovTech.</li><li>Promote a strong cybersecurity culture through organisation-wide awareness initiatives.</li><li>Serve as the key cybersecurity advisor to executive and clinical leaders.</li><li>Develop and lead high-performing security teams to uphold organisational cybersecurity excellence.</li></ul><p></p></p><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li>Min Master's Degree IT, Computer Science or related field</li><li>Minimum of 20 years' of Cybersecurity experience in healthcare setting</li><li>Possess certifications in CISSP, CCSP, CCSK, CGEIT, PMP is a MUST</li><li>Working experience in healthcare regulations including PDPA, Cybersecurity Act, and compliance frameworks </li></ul><p>Interested candidates who wish to apply for the advertised position, please click APPLY NOW or email an updated copy of your resume/cv.</p><p>We regret that only shortlisted candidate will be notified.</p><p><strong>Email Address: Jobs@recruitpedia.sg</strong></p><ul><li>EA License No: 19C9682</li><li>EA Personnel No: R2198636</li><li>EA Personnel Name: Oh Puey Xin</li></ul>",
